    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那这三个和IssuerKit是什么关系？我理解为IssuerKit是一个工厂产物，把Mint、Issuer、Brand打包在一起？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IssuerKit",
