      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把IssuerKit作为中心类，用组合关系连接Mint、Issuer、Brand。然后添加ertp模块，标注makeIssuerKit返回IssuerKit。",
      "elements_involved": [
